  "prompt": "If I go to sprint and ask for a free iPhone if I switch will they do it?",
  "response": "At Sprint (which merged with T-Mobile), promotions and deals can vary over time. Occasionally, carriers offer deals like free phones for new customers who switch from another provider, often with certain conditions such as trading in an eligible device, signing up for a specific plan, or maintaining service for a certain period.\n\nIf you're interested in switching to T-Mobile and want to know if they currently have promotions for a free iPhone, it\u2019s best to check their website or contact their customer service directly. They can provide you with the latest information and any available offers or requirements.",
